{
  "chapter": 30,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十回 大漠之夜\n\n噶伦喇嘛在禅房中持剑欲杀波娃，危急时刻卜鹰以小方的\"魔眼\"剑脱手飞掷救下波娃，随后与噶伦展开一场惊天剑斗。卜鹰剑术精绝，噶伦虽身剑合一却急于求胜，最终主动放下宝剑\"赤松\"，在战后重入禅境悟道。卜鹰告诉小方，噶伦并非败于剑下，而是借此激发剑气、宣泄心中戾气以求悟道。\n\n卜鹰带小方深入大漠，来到初遇波娃的风化岩石间，掘出吕三失劫的三十万两黄金。卜鹰坦承自己就是猫盗首领，截下黄金是为了阻止吕三以拜火教取代藏地佛教的阴谋。波娃为族人甘愿潜入吕三组织做奸细，甚至不惜牺牲小方以取得信任。小方得知真相后心如死灰，躺在星光下默默承受。最后班察巴那现身，道出一路暗中护送的真相，暗示无人能泄漏他们的秘密。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "text": "恭喜大师。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "为何恭喜？何喜之有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "text": "大师已在剑中悟道。恭喜大师修为又有精进。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "你好。你去。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ga_lun_la_ma",
      "speaker_name": "噶伦喇嘛",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "为何要你去？为何我不能去？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "他没有败。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "就是败了，也不是败在我的剑下。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "绝对不是！他败，只因为他根本没有杀我的意思，只不过想用我激发他的剑气，泄出他心中的戾气与杀机。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "他根本没有胜我之意，又怎么能算是败？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我知道你心里有个打不开的结。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "如果你真想知道其中的秘密，就跟我走，可是我劝你，有些事还是不知道的好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "我们什么时候再往前走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我们不再往前走了。这里就是我们的地头。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "你带我到这里来于什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "现在你总该明白我为什么要带你到这里来了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "是你埋在这里的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是我。我就是猫盗。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我们那队伍里，每个人都是猫盗，他们才真正是久经训练、百战不死的战士，卫天鹏属下那些人跟他们比起来，只能算是初学刀剑的孩子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "卫天鹏找不到这批黄金，因为他想不到我们根本不想将这批黄金运出沙漠。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "永远都不想运出去！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "永远！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我们并不想要这批黄金，我们截下来，只不过因为我们也不能让吕三他们利用这批黄金去对付别人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "别人？别人是些什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "就是这两天你天天都能看得见的那些人。也就是波娃，班察巴那他们的族人和姐妹兄弟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "吕三为什么要对付他们？准备怎么样去对付他们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "他要推翻藏人已信奉数百年的宗教，要刺杀藏人心目中的活佛，要在这里建立他自己的霸业。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "但是这里宗教信仰已在藏人心中根深蒂固，所以吕三这计划如果实现了，西藏境内必将永无宁日。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "所以你们不能让他的计划实现。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "绝不能！为了阻挠他，我们也不择一切手段，不惜牺牲一切。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "第一个牺牲的就是波娃。牺牲最大的就是她。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "她才是班察巴那说的那个为了族人而牺牲自己的女人？不惜牺牲一切潜伏到吕三那组织内部去做奸细？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不错，她是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这秘密我们绝不能让别人知道，所以在那不祥的'黑羽之帐'中，我只有让你误会她，在'死颈'外那一战中，我们也绝不能让她走出第三顶轿子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "所以噶伦才肯让她住在布达拉宫，所以你才会去救她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为我绝不能让她死在噶伦手里，又不能让噶伦抱憾终生。为了噶伦的宗教，她的牺牲已太大。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "她非但不惜自己，甚至不惜牺牲她所心爱的人。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你可以考虑，是留下来跟我在一起，还是走？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "我会考虑。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "随便你要考虑多久，但是你决定的时候，一定要先来告诉我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "你做事一向极谨慎，可是这次却做得太冒险了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "冒险？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "你不怕有人跟踪我们到这里来？不怕别人发现这儿的藏金？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "他不怕有人跟踪，因为他知道这一路上我都在你们的附近，就算有条狐狸想跟踪你们，我也已抓住了它，剥下了它的皮。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ban_cha_ba_na",
      "speaker_name": "班察巴那",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "他当然也不怕你会泄漏他的秘密。从来没有人能泄漏我们的秘密。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 342
    }
  ],
